nette. Foliot circulaire \u00e0 un bras. Coq ovale \u00e0 un pied reperc\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurettes ; piliers en forme de balustres.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; Mouvement sign\u00e9 : No\u00ebl Hubert \/ au gros horloge \/ ARouen. Poin\u00e7on sur la t\u00eate du pendant (oeil : d\u00e9charge des menus ouvrages d\u0027or et d\u0027argent vieux, Paris, 1750-1756 ?).","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Longueur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"2,8","displayDimension":"2,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2","displayDimension":"2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche","placeOfCreation":"Rouen (Haute-Normandie = Haute Normandie-\u003ESeine-Maritime = Seine Maritime)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 584 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Olivier, Marie-Julie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Olivier, Jules-Ren\u00e9","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"24\/01\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"05\/02\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"04\/08\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935}]}],"o